content: How do we report a concerning post on one of our channels?
You can tag @ moderator or @ community moderator. If it's in a specific community (like text, call, etc) you can tag that moderator group the same way.
if you don't want to share with a whole team of mods, you can DM an individual who has one of those roles.
Hi, <@1272714435848310784>! You can dm any of us here, if you'd like!
